Leaves with petiole 0.9-1.7 cm and blade subcoriaceous to coriaceous, 5-11 by 2.5-5.8 cm, elliptic or ovate-elliptic, rarely broadly or narrowly elliptic, with the base acute or rarely somewhat truncate and the apex acute or rarely obtuse;
