					submerged leaves lanceolate to oblong, petiolate, sometimes the lower ones reduced to phyllodes, lamina 50-150 by 15-30 mm, 9-13-veined, margin serrulate toward the tip, base cuneate, apex mucronate;
					petioles 3-12(-20) mm;
					stipules axillary, convolute, 25-50 mm, obtuse or rounded at apex.

